                                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Paramount+ Is Finally Getting Sports Multiview]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/paramount-is-finally-getting-sports-multiview/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/four-soccer-games-being-played-at-the-same-time-on-paramount.jpg" length="201" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Streaming]]></category><category><![CDATA[Paramount Plus]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Just in time for another Champions League.
